Author: baronofficiall2
Title: [ANN][ICO] Dbrain — a blockchain platform to collectively build AI apps
Body: What is this DBRAIN? The DBRAIN platform is a platform based on Blockchain designed to offer artificial intelligence applications to individuals with smartphone capabilities to provide easy and reliable use for you. As a result of the great effort of teaching data that 80% of artificial intelligence is made up of data and planned to be transferred to the machine, this corresponds to a long time period and we face temporal problems. The DBRAIN platform has initiated this probing solution process. For experts and field workers in the data field, we have developed a tool to simply transfer the natural data to be translated into machine power. the hard work on this side was removed and the transactions were made faster and easier.  System Working Principle The DBRAIN platform provides a fair revenue distribution feature with a blockchain base and its own DBR token, which provides transparent use. The reliability of the system is also ensured. DBR is an official token that provides services to you while using artificial intelligence in the system. Another application included in the system in the name of security measures is the PICARD application. this application provides data confidentiality so that private data and income can be controlled in the future. The DBRAIN platform will form a scalable basis to increase the accessibility of systems with high quality ratios in the artificial intelligence field. DBRAIN stands out with many convenience and security measures. This platform brings together many applications such as object detection, face recognition, classification, voice recognition, data analysis.  As a result, we will evaluate the project in general terms; The DBRAIN platform has become a very important application for artificial intelligence, and it has become important for the participants to keep their expectations at a high level.

Author: dBrain
Title: [ANN][ICO] Dbrain — a blockchain platform to collectively build AI apps
Body: Hey guys,  Many thanks to all of you who expressed their interest in what we have been doing! Your words mean a lot to us, are highly appreciated, and all in all, prove we are on the right track!  Dbrain coin sale is coming soon and all the details are about to be published, including the white paper, and you'll be among the very first to know once it happens! Please make sure to follow us here on Bitcointalk, subscribe to our mailing list, join our other channels like Telegram, Twitter, Facebook, Medium – whichever appears to be more convenient for you.  Everyone is welcome to support us within the framework of our bounty campaign kindly managed by the awesome Bountyhive team and ColorlessK in particular. Check out the Dbrain bounty thread and please feel free to ask all bounty-related questions right there.    We are glad that you have already tried our Telegram bot! We will launch tasks for various audiences, skills and professions. Currently, there is a test task uploaded which is basically aimed to help us test the platform, reveal possible bugs, and so on. Stay tuned! By the way, we already have not only a Telegram bot but also web Alpha is available to try.  AI happens!
